OL,3,CShoplifting in England and Wales soars
OL,4,Cto highest since police records began
OL,6,FAntoine Allen reports on the rise of
OL,7,Fshoplifting in England and Wales.
OL,9,FShoplifting across England and Wales
OL,10,Fsoared to the highest level since
OL,11,Fpolice record began, according to new
OL,12,Ffigures released on Thursday.
OL,14,FData from the Office for National
OL,15,FStatistics (ONS) shows shoplifting
OL,16,Foffences rose by 20% compared with the
OL,17,Fprevious year and figures are the
OL,18,Fhighest since current police recording
OL,19,Fpractices began in March 2003.
