OL,3,CShoplifting in England and Wales soars
OL,4,Cto highest since police records began
OL,6,FPolicing Minister, Diana Johnson,
OL,7,Fsays: "There is work going on with
OL,8,Fpolicing, there is resourcing going
OL,9,Fon, I had a retail crime summit with
OL,10,Fbig retailers at the end of last year
OL,11,Fto see what more we can do together to
OL,12,Fmap what's happening on our high
OL,13,Fstreets."
OL,15,FThe data shows 516,971 offences this
OL,16,Fyear, compared to 429,873 last year,
OL,17,Fthe highest number on record.
