OL,3,CShoplifting in England and Wales soars
OL,4,Cto highest since police records began
OL,6,FShoplifting offences in London also
OL,7,Frose sharply last year, with nearly
OL,8,F90,000 incidents recorded in the 12
OL,9,Fmonths to December 2024.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police recorded
OL,12,F88,248 offences, while the City of
OL,13,FLondon Police reported 1,573 cases - a
OL,14,F61% increase.
OL,16,FRetailers are investing tens of
OL,17,Fthousands to protect their stores -
OL,18,Finstalling reinforced doors, CCTV and
OL,19,Ffog deterrents.
