OL,3,CShoplifting in England and Wales soars
OL,4,Cto highest since police records began
OL,6,FITV News spoke to Kensington shop
OL,7,Fowner Hanushka Toni who runs the
OL,8,Fluxury retailer Sellier.
OL,10,FShe said: "The security for the new
OL,11,Fstore is coming in at just under
OL,12,F#100k. The front door alone is costing
OL,13,F#65,000. If we don't look after our
OL,14,Fown security, no one else will."
OL,16,FDespite these efforts, her anxiety
OL,17,Fremains high.
