OL,6,FThe data shows that London saw the
OL,7,Fhighest increase from the previous
OL,8,Fyear at 54% - something the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police are trying to
OL,10,Ftackle.
OL,12,FA sting operation in South London
OL,13,Frecovered around #150,000 of suspected
OL,14,Fstolen goods and led to eight arrests.
OL,16,FSecurity officer Sunday described a
OL,17,Fterrifying encounter that he
OL,18,Fexperienced.
